paragraphs.title: FB_Live_9Mar
paragraphs.text:
cacheTempView(sql="
select distinct * 
from
    (select distinct *
                    ,row_number() over(partition by dmPublisherInfoId order by timestamp desc) as row 
    from `sinceLast180Days(dmPublisherInfo)`
    where tenant = 'FACEBOOK' AND TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000)) >= '2023-02-22'  AND TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000))<= '2023-03-09')tt
where row = 1 
","temp.FB_Live_9Mar")

select distinct * 
from

    from `sinceLast180Days(dmPublisherInfo)`

where row = 1 
","temp.FB_Live_")

paragraphs.title: 9Mar
paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
with cte as(
    select a.date, a.pogId, a.subOrderId, b.Channel 
    from (
            select a.pogId, b.subOrderId, to_date(FROM_UNIXTIME((b.orderDate)/1000)) as date 
            from `temp.availPog` a left join `last14Days(agCmDump)` b 
            on a.pogId=b.pogId 
            where to_date(FROM_UNIXTIME((b.orderDate)/1000))>='2023-03-02' and to_date(FROM_UNIXTIME((b.orderDate)/1000))<='2023-03-08'
        ) a 
    left join `temp.final_attri2` b 
    on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId
)

select date, count(distinct subOrderId) as SD_Orders, count(distinct case when lower(Channel) like 'fb%' then subOrderId end) as FB_Orders 
from cte 
group by date 
order by date desc
",1000)

paragraphs.title: NMSO
paragraphs.text:
cacheTempView(sql="
select pogMarketingFeedBaseTab as pogId
        ,sum(bauNmpu*pogWeightage)/sum(pogWeightage) as NMSO
        ,sum(bauNmpu*pogWeightage*(1-cancellationPer))/sum(pogWeightage) as NMBO
        ,sum((bauNmpu-totalFixedFfcMarketingFeedBaseTab+laapFixedFfcMarketingFeedBaseTab)*pogWeightage)/sum(pogWeightage) as NM3SO
        ,sum((bauNmpu-totalFixedFfcMarketingFeedBaseTab+laapFixedFfcMarketingFeedBaseTab)*pogWeightage*(1-cancellationPer))/sum(pogWeightage) as NM3BO
from(
    select distinct *
    from marketingFeedBaseTable
    ) a

group by pogMarketingFeedBaseTab
","temp.nmso_bau")
